title: Taylor Swift & Gigi Hadid Rock Out to 'I Don't Wanna Live Forever' Together (Video)
text:
Taylor Swift ‘s most recent song “I Don’t Wanna Live Forever” may be a huge hit, but she hadn’t heard it on the radio until today! 
While cruising through NYC with her BFF Gigi Hadid , the 26-year-old superstar heard the song for the first time. 
“First time listening to it on the radio, I’ve never heard it before,” Taylor said with a huge grin. 
Tay and Gigi , whose boyfriend Zayn Malik is also featured on the song, proceeded to have a dance party while jamming out in the car!
Check out the super cute video below…
Also pictured: Gigi heading out of her apartment on Wednesday (February 1) in New York City.
